These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
House: cape-cod, palace
1. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Flower      | aconite     | tulip      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| House   | cape-cod  | palace      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
2 different games are played: chess, bridge
City: boston, miami
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
3. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
4. the person traveling to boston is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Game         | bridge | chess   |
| City   | boston               | miami  |

 #################################

 
